title: Michelle Wolf | The Kind of Story We Need Right Now: 82-year-old Bodybuilder Beat up Burglar
description:
Seth steps away from bleak and depressing news to share a news story about an 82-year-old female bodybuilder who beat up a burglar who tried to break into her home.

Michelle Wolf talks about Joe Biden and who she wants to get a massage from. Plus, she reviews some jokes that she recently sent to Seth for his monologue.
